column2: Brady John Haran OAM (born 18 June 1976) is an Australian-British independent filmmaker and video journalist who produces educational videos and documentary films for his YouTube channels; the most notable being Periodic Videos and Numberphile. Haran is also the co-host of the Hello Internet podcast along with fellow educational YouTuber CGP Grey. On 22 August 2017; Haran launched his second podcast; called The Unmade Podcast; and on 11 November 2018; he launched his third podcast; The Numberphile Podcast; based on his mathematics-centered channel of the same name.
